sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_7e91b1efdb33af009ee09a82ca9619f6
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1001191</definition_id><description>Monthly Breakdown of  10 Slowest Average Probe Execution Times in Current Build</description><exec_time_threshold>5000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>Monthly Breakdown of  10 Slowest Average Probe Execution Times in Current Build</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var build, rollUpEnabled, indEnabled;
answer = JSON.stringify(buildSlowProbeJSON());

function buildSlowProbeJSON() {
	var result = {};
	var buildTag, buildDate;

	// Find buildTag
	var reusedGr = new GlideRecord('sys_properties');
	reusedGr.query('name', 'glide.buildtag.last');
	if (reusedGr.next())
		buildTag = reusedGr.getValue('value');
	
	// Find buildDate
	reusedGr = new GlideRecord('sys_properties');
	reusedGr.query('name', 'glide.builddate.last');
	if (reusedGr.next())
		buildDate = reusedGr.getValue('value');

	// Return empty result if build/version not found
	if (buildTag && buildDate)
		build = buildTag + '_' + buildDate;
	else
		return result;
	
	// Find rollup-by-build toggle
	reusedGr = new GlideRecord('sys_properties');
	reusedGr.query('name', 'glide.discovery.perf.metrics.rollup_by_build');
	if (reusedGr.next())
		rollUpEnabled = reusedGr.getValue('value');

	// Find Individual Metric toggle
	reusedGr = new GlideRecord('sys_properties');
	reusedGr.query('name', 'glide.discovery.perf.metrics.enable_collection');
	if (reusedGr.next())
		indEnabled = reusedGr.getValue('value');

	// If rollup-by-build exists, we try the rollup-by-build table
	if (rollUpEnabled)
		useRollUpTable(result);

	// Extra fields added to resulting JSON if populated
	if (result['count'] >= 0) {
		result['current_build_version'] = build;
		result['glide.discovery.perf.metrics.rollup_by_build'] = rollUpEnabled;
		result['glide.discovery.perf.metrics.enable_collection'] = indEnabled;
	}
	
	return result;
}

function useRollUpTable(result) {
	if (!GlideTableDescriptor.isValid('discovery_perf_metric_probe_sensor_rollup_by_build'))
		return result;
	
	var arrayOfMappings = [];
	var i = 1;
	
	var rollUpGr = new GlideRecord('discovery_perf_metric_probe_sensor_rollup_by_build');
	// Do not include 'Horizontal Pattern'
	rollUpGr.addQuery('probe', '!=', '4f64c6389f230200fe2ab0aec32e7068');
	rollUpGr.addQuery('build_version', build);
	rollUpGr.orderByDesc('probe_time_average');
	rollUpGr.setLimit(10);
	rollUpGr.query();
	while(rollUpGr.next()) {
		arrayOfMappings.push({
			probe: {
					name: rollUpGr.getDisplayValue('probe'),
					sys_id: rollUpGr.getValue('probe'),
					ecc_queue_topic: rollUpGr.getValue('ecc_queue_topic'),
					ecc_queue_name: rollUpGr.getValue('ecc_queue_name')
					},
			avg_time_ms: parseFloat(rollUpGr.getValue('probe_time_average')),
			rank: i++
		});
	}
	
	result['avg_slowest_probes_in_current_build'] = arrayOfMappings;
	result['count'] = arrayOfMappings.length;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-01 09:46:42</sys_created_on><sys_id>7e91b1efdb33af009ee09a82ca9619f6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1001191</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_7e91b1efdb33af009ee09a82ca9619f6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-06-10 12:17:38</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_bed72123db73af009ee09a82ca9619b4
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1001190</definition_id><description>Breakdown of CMDB by Class where Source is Discovery. It is possible for a CI to belong to more than one ci_class.</description><exec_time_threshold>10000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>Monthly Breakdown of CMDB Count By Class [Source is Discovery]</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = JSON.stringify(constructCISourceJSON());

function constructCISourceJSON() {
	var result = {};
	if (!GlideTableDescriptor.isValid('sys_object_source'))
		return result;

	if (!GlideTableDescriptor.isValid('cmdb'))
		return result;

	// Count of unique tables (CI classes)
	var uniqueTableCount = 0;
	var arrayOfMappings = [];

	// Generates the CI class to count mapping
	var gr = new GlideAggregate('sys_object_source');
	gr.addNotNullQuery('target_table');
	gr.addNotNullQuery('target_sys_id');
	gr.addQuery('id', 'Discovery');
	gr.addJoinQuery('cmdb', 'target_sys_id', 'sys_id');
	gr.groupBy('target_table');
	gr.addAggregate('count(distinct','target_sys_id');
	gr.query();
	while(gr.next()) {
		arrayOfMappings.push({
			ci_class: gr.getValue('target_table'),
			count: parseInt(gr.getAggregate('count(distinct','target_sys_id'))
		});
		uniqueTableCount++;
	}

	result['cmdb_data_discovery_source'] = arrayOfMappings;
	result['count'] = uniqueTableCount;
	return result;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-01 09:04:06</sys_created_on><sys_id>bed72123db73af009ee09a82ca9619b4</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1001190</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_bed72123db73af009ee09a82ca9619b4</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-06-10 12:17:38</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type>count</agg_type><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1000532</definition_id><description>count of distinct product owners who own personal backlogs. This is a new table which has been added in this release where only product owners can define personal backlogs.</description><exec_time_threshold>500</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>distinctProductOwnerCount</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = getDistintProductOwnerCount();

function getDistintProductOwnerCount () {
	var gr = new GlideAggregate('backlog_definition');
	if(!gr.isValid())
		return 0;
	gr.groupBy('owner');
	gr.addAggregate('count');
	gr.query();
	return gr.getRowCount();
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-09-20 16:36:14</sys_created_on><sys_id>6b719542db55030074f279daae9619c8</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1000532</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_6b719542db55030074f279daae9619c8</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:58</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type>count</agg_type><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1002170</definition_id><description>Number of designated shift managers</description><exec_time_threshold>5000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>Number of designated shift managers</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = getDesignatedShiftManagers();
/*
* Count the number of designated shift managers
*/
function getDesignatedShiftManagers() {
	var count = 0;
	var gr = new GlideRecord('on_call_group_preference');
	gr.setCategory("usage");
	gr.addNotNullQuery('rota_managers');
	gr.query();

	while (gr.next())
		count = count + gr.rota_managers.getDisplayValue().split(',').length;

	return count;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-09-24 17:24:15</sys_created_on><sys_id>a76bd95adbcc84103fcbe1d3ca961928</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1002170</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_a76bd95adbcc84103fcbe1d3ca961928</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:57</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_6505cc441bcbb70066fe4225bd4bcbc9
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1001513</definition_id><description>number of surveys defined that the survey content can be embedded in email</description><exec_time_threshold>50</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>getOAMSurvey</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = getOAMSurvey();

/*
* Count the number of surveys that can be embedded in the Outlook email  
* plugin com.sn_ms_oam needs to be installed, otherwise ms_adaptive_cards field doesn't exist.
*/
function getOAMSurvey() {
    // check OAM Plugin installed
    if (!GlidePluginManager.isActive("com.sn_ms_oam"))
        return 0;
    
    var count = 0;
    var agg = new GlideAggregate('asmt_metric_type');
	if (!agg.isValid())
		return 0;
    agg.addEncodedQuery('evaluation_method=survey^active=true^notify_user=true^ms_adaptive_cards=true');
    agg.addAggregate('COUNT');
    agg.setWorkflow(false);
    agg.query();
          
    if (agg.next())
        count = agg.getAggregate('COUNT');

    return count;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-07-29 18:17:38</sys_created_on><sys_id>6505cc441bcbb70066fe4225bd4bcbc9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1001513</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_6505cc441bcbb70066fe4225bd4bcbc9</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:57</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000263</definition_id><description>Maximum number of project funding records by portfolio and fiscal year</description><exec_time_threshold>3000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>1</license_model><name>max_project_funding_records_by_portfolio_and_fiscal_year</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = getMaxProjectFundingCount();

function getMaxProjectFundingCount() {
	var ga = new GlideAggregate('project_funding');
	ga.addAggregate('COUNT');
	ga.addNotNullQuery('portfolio');
	ga.addNotNullQuery('task');
	ga.groupBy('portfolio');
	ga.groupBy('fiscal_period.fiscal_year');
	ga.query();
	
	var maxRecords = 0;
	while (ga.next()) {
		var recordCount = ga.getAggregate('COUNT');
		if (!gs.nil(recordCount) && parseInt(recordCount) > maxRecords)
			maxRecords = parseInt(recordCount);
	}
	
	return maxRecords;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-02-27 11:34:39</sys_created_on><sys_id>f3d950049319320064f572edb67ffb0c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>5</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000263</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_f3d950049319320064f572edb67ffb0c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-06-10 12:17:39</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_89c6ed23db73af009ee09a82ca961943
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1001189</definition_id><description>Breakdown of CMDB by Class where Source is ALL. It is possible for a CI to belong to more than one ci_class.</description><exec_time_threshold>10000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>Monthly Breakdown of CMDB Count By Class [All Sources]</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = JSON.stringify(constructCISourceJSON());

function constructCISourceJSON() {
	var result = {};
	if (!GlideTableDescriptor.isValid('sys_object_source'))
		return result;
	
	if (!GlideTableDescriptor.isValid('cmdb'))
		return result;
	
	// Count of unique tables (CI classes)
	var uniqueTableCount = 0;
	var arrayOfMappings = [];
	
	// Generates the CI class to count mapping
	var gr = new GlideAggregate('sys_object_source');
	gr.addNotNullQuery('target_table');
	gr.addNotNullQuery('target_sys_id');
	gr.addJoinQuery('cmdb', 'target_sys_id', 'sys_id');
	gr.groupBy('target_table');
	gr.addAggregate('count(distinct','target_sys_id');
	gr.query();
	while(gr.next()) {
		arrayOfMappings.push({
			ci_class: gr.getValue('target_table'),
			count: parseInt(gr.getAggregate('count(distinct','target_sys_id'))
		});
		uniqueTableCount++;
	}
	
	result['cmdb_data_all_source'] = arrayOfMappings;
	result['count'] = uniqueTableCount;
	return result;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-01 08:59:20</sys_created_on><sys_id>89c6ed23db73af009ee09a82ca961943</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1001189</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_89c6ed23db73af009ee09a82ca961943</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-06-10 12:17:38</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1001201</definition_id><description>Determine if instance is configured with ADME enabled or not.</description><exec_time_threshold>1000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>Monthly Query of Instance Configuration [ADME Enabled or Not]</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = JSON.stringify(getInstanceConfigForADME());

function getInstanceConfigForADME() {
	var result = {};

	if (!GlideTableDescriptor.isValid('sys_properties'))
		return result;

	var count = 0;
	var value = '';

	var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_properties');
	gr.addQuery('name', 'glide.discovery.enable_adme');
	gr.query();
	if (gr.next()) {
		value = gr.value + '';
		count++;
	}
	result['instance_config'] = [{'glide.discovery.enable_adme':value}];
	result['count'] = count;

	return result;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-07 00:08:00</sys_created_on><sys_id>dcb6a619db08b3409ee09a82ca961908</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1001201</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_dcb6a619db08b3409ee09a82ca961908</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-06-10 12:17:38</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sysevent_script_action_d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sysevent_script_action"><sysevent_script_action action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><condition_script/><description/><event_name>login.failed</event_name><name>SNC User Lockout Check with Auto Unlock</name><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[//
// Check to see if the user has failed to login too many times
// when the limit is reached, lock the user out of the system.
// Also create a trigger to unlock the user after 'N' minutes.
//

lockoutOnFailedLogin();

function lockoutOnFailedLogin() {
	var maxUnlockAttempts = gs.getProperty("glide.user.max_unlock_attempts", 5);
	var gr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
	if (gr.get("user_name", event.parm1.toString())) {
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts)
			return;

		gr.failed_attempts += 1;
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts) {
			gr.locked_out = true;
			gr.update();
			gs.log("User " + event.parm1 + " locked out due to too many invalid login attempts");
			triggerUnlock(gr.sys_id);
		} else {
			gr.update();       
		}
	}
}

function triggerUnlock(userSysID) {
	var unlockIn = gs.getProperty("glide.user.unlock_timeout_in_mins", 15);
	var trigger = new GlideRecord("sys_trigger");
	trigger.name = "Unlock the user after "+ unlockIn + " mins";
	trigger.next_action = getTriggerTime(unlockIn);
	trigger.job_id.setDisplayValue('RunScriptJob');
	trigger.script = getTriggerScript(userSysID);
	trigger.document = 'sys_user';
	trigger.document_key = userSysID;
	trigger.state = 0;
	trigger.trigger_type = 0;
	trigger.insert();
}

function getTriggerScript(userSysID) {
	var ret = ""
	+ "var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('sys_id', '" +userSysID+ "');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('locked_out', true);\n"
	+ "gr.query();\n"
	+ "if (gr.next()) {\n"
		+ "gr.locked_out = false;\n"
		+ "gr.failed_attempts = 0;\n"
		+ "gr.update();\n"
		+ "gs.log('Auto-unlocking user '+gr.name);\n"
	+ "} else {\n"
		+ "gs.log('Unable to auto-unlock user with sys_id: "+userSysID+"');\n"
	+ "}";
	return ret;
}

function getTriggerTime(minutesToAdd) {
	var checkTime = new GlideDateTime(/*now*/);
	checkTime.addSeconds(minutesToAdd * 60);
	return checkTime;
}
]]></script><synchronous>true</synchronous><sys_class_name>sysevent_script_action</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2013-08-24 00:27:47</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567</sys_id><sys_mod_count>28</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SNC User Lockout Check with Auto Unlock</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="High Security Settings" source="com.glide.high_security">a9e7329d07c20010944dfc018c1ed0a7</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysevent_script_action_d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-12-30 08:44:38</sys_updated_on></sysevent_script_action></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_fix_c7463eea07968410944dfc018c1ed0ac
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_fix"><sys_script_fix action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><before>false</before><description/><flush_cache>false</flush_cache><name>Create Stories to replicate behaviour</name><record_for_rollback>false</record_for_rollback><run_once>true</run_once><script><![CDATA[replicate("1771a6e207568410944dfc018c1ed0b6", 7, 350);

function replicate (source, nstart, niterations){
	var fields = "project,theme,product,priority,type,story_points,short_description,acceptance_criteria,description,assignment_group,correlation_id,release,epic,assigned_to";
	var fieldsDup = fields.split(',');

	var current = new GlideRecord("rm_story");
	// ID from the story
	current.get(source);

	var count = nstart;
	while (count < niterations){
	var gr = new GlideRecord('rm_story');
		gr.initialize();
		for(i=0;i<fieldsDup.length;i++){
			if(fieldsDup[i]=='short_description')
				gr.setValue(fieldsDup[i],current.getValue(fieldsDup[i])+' ' + count);
			else {
				if(fieldsDup[i]=='description')
					gr.setValue(fieldsDup[i],current.getValue(fieldsDup[i])+' ' + count);
				else
					gr.setValue(fieldsDup[i],current.getValue(fieldsDup[i]));
			}
		}
		var newid = gr.insert();
		count ++;
		gs.info("We insert " + count);
		GlideSysAttachment.copy('rm_story',current.sys_id,'rm_story',newid);
	}

}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_fix</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-01-15 15:01:53</sys_created_on><sys_id>c7463eea07968410944dfc018c1ed0ac</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Create Stories to replicate behaviour</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_fix_c7463eea07968410944dfc018c1ed0ac</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-15 15:10:22</sys_updated_on><unloadable>false</unloadable></sys_script_fix></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1001223</definition_id><description>Maximum monthly IntegrationHub transactions in last 12 months.</description><exec_time_threshold>5000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>ua_ih_usage_max_compliance</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var aggregator = new IHUsageMetricsAggregator();
var sums = aggregator.getTransactionCountByMonth(true);
var maxCount = 0;
while (sums.next()) {  
  var currentCount = parseInt(sums.getAggregate('SUM', 'use_count'));
  if(currentCount > maxCount) 
    maxCount = currentCount;
}
answer = maxCount;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-19 18:33:56</sys_created_on><sys_id>21e650a9dbd8f70020df9f5faa9619af</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1001223</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_21e650a9dbd8f70020df9f5faa9619af</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:56</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type>count</agg_type><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1002212</definition_id><description>Shifts with Rotate through members Escalation type</description><exec_time_threshold>5000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>Shifts with Rotate through members Escalation type</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = getRotateThroughMemberShifts();

/*
* Count the number of shifts with Rotate through members Escalation type
*/
function getRotateThroughMemberShifts() {
	var rowCount = 0;
	var gr = new GlideRecord('cmn_rota');
	gr.setCategory("usage");
	gr.addActiveQuery();
	gr.query();

	while (gr.next()) {
		var gr1 = new GlideRecord('cmn_rota_roster');
		gr1.setCategory("usage");
		gr1.addActiveQuery();
		gr1.addQuery('rota', gr.sys_id);
		gr1.query();
		if (gr.use_custom_escalation == false && gr1.getRowCount() == 1)
			rowCount++;
	}
	return rowCount;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-09-30 15:59:28</sys_created_on><sys_id>5491c850db18c0103fcbe1d3ca9619c0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1002212</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_5491c850db18c0103fcbe1d3ca9619c0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:56</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type>count</agg_type><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000261</definition_id><description>Max custom console configurations for any user</description><exec_time_threshold>3000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>max_custom_console_configurations_for_any_user</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var maxConfigs = 0;

var ga = new GlideAggregate('planned_task_custom_console');
ga.groupBy('owner');
ga.addAggregate('COUNT');
ga.query();

while(ga.next()) {
	if(parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT')) > maxConfigs) {
		maxConfigs = parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT'));
	}
}

answer = maxConfigs;

sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_6ab3a6dedb55030066e778b5ae9619f5
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type>count</agg_type><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1000533</definition_id><description>Get MIN, MAX, AVG and total count for sprints grouped by assignment group</description><exec_time_threshold>2000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>getUsageDataForSprints</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = getUsageDataForSprints();

function getUsageDataForSprints () {
	var arr = [];
	var total = 0;
	var usageAnalyticsData = {};
		var gr = new GlideAggregate('rm_sprint');
		if(!gr.isValid())
			return 0;
		gr.addQuery('active','true');
		gr.groupBy('assignment_group');
		gr.addAggregate('count');
		gr.query();
		while(gr.next()){
			arr.push(gr.getAggregate('count'));
			total += parseInt(gr.getAggregate('count'));
		}
		
		usageAnalyticsData["count"] = total;
		usageAnalyticsData["MAX"] = Math.max.apply(null, arr);
		usageAnalyticsData["MIN"] = Math.min.apply(null, arr);
		if(arr.length>0)
			usageAnalyticsData["AVG"] = total/(arr.length);
		
		return (new JSON().encode(usageAnalyticsData));
	}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-09-21 17:14:00</sys_created_on><sys_id>6ab3a6dedb55030066e778b5ae9619f5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1000533</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_6ab3a6dedb55030066e778b5ae9619f5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:58</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_ec6815980bd13200b7d0c32c15673a3f
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type>count</agg_type><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000260</definition_id><description>Max number of shares for any console</description><exec_time_threshold>3000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>0</license_model><name>max_number_of_shares_for_any_console</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var maxShares = 0;

var ga = new GlideAggregate('planned_task_custom_console_member');
ga.groupBy('console');
ga.addAggregate('COUNT');
ga.query();

while(ga.next()) {
	if(parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT')) > maxShares) {
		maxShares = parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT'));
	}
}

answer = maxShares;
]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-02-28 10:31:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>ec6815980bd13200b7d0c32c15673a3f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000260</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_ec6815980bd13200b7d0c32c15673a3f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:59</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><agg_col/><agg_type/><count_type>Licensing</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000401</definition_id><description>Maximum transactions in last 12 months</description><exec_time_threshold>5000</exec_time_threshold><group_by/><license_model>1</license_model><name>outbound_usage_metrics_max_compliance</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var aggregator = new OutboundUsageMetricsAggregator();
var sums = aggregator.getTransactionCountByMonth('sys_hub_step_instance', true);
var maxCount = 0;
while (sums.next()) {  
  var currentCount = parseInt(sums.getAggregate('SUM', 'agg_value'));
  if(currentCount > maxCount) 
    maxCount = currentCount;
}
answer = maxCount;


]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-08-10 00:09:40</sys_created_on><sys_id>d736a2a4e720030007a64caac2f6a93a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>18</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000401</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">f163361907020010944dfc018c1ed052</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_d736a2a4e720030007a64caac2f6a93a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-29 16:51:59</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>true</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>ecc_queue</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Pre-G MID Upgrade ECC Blocker</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
	var query = current.getEncodedQuery();
	if (query.indexOf('agent') != -1) {
		var agent = '';
		var queryArr = query.split('^');
		for (var i = 0; i < queryArr.length; i++)
			if (queryArr[i].indexOf('agent') != -1)
				agent = queryArr[i].split('=')[1];
		
		var mid = MIDServer.getByName(agent);

		if (mid && mid.isPreGeneva())
			current.addQuery('topic', 'IN', ['SystemCommand', 'HeartbeatProbe']);
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>will.swift</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-03-03 23:49:05</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Pre-G MID Upgrade ECC Blocker</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="MID Server" source="com.glideapp.agent">8be6bad507c20010944dfc018c1ed065</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-01-30 07:35:58</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5"/></record_update>
